<p>
See how you can run <a class="wiki" href="/wiki/CherryPy">CherryPy</a> <a class="ext-link" href="http://www.defuze.org/archives/228-running-cherrypy-on-android-with-sl4a.html"><span class="icon"></span>on the Android platform</a> to serve your web application from your mobile phone.
</p>
</div> 

